title: The Healthy Deli
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located within a natural foods store. Sandwich bar, juice bar, and deli counter. Food items include a blackened tofu wrap, veggie wrap made with vegenaise, vegan chik'n salad wrap made with TVP, and deli salads. Also made-to-order items including a vegetarian breakfast wrap, smoothies and wheatgrass shots.
